description: I noticed him already a couple of minutes before. But as he looked very young I didn´t approach him at the first place. Just when I listened him calling a friend for a party in a club I had to try my luck and to find out his age. His name was Tomas, and he was 18, almost 19 to be correct. And a real cutie. He just moved to Prague to study Economics. Living from part-time jobs and the support of his family he showed some interest in my dirty offer. And I didn´t hesitate to make him an offer he couldn´t resist. He even couldn´t believe that someone would pay him for a blowjob. Yes, he didn´t even realize how cute he was. On the way to the hotel I asked him to show me his ID card - one more time checking that my luck was true. And later in the hotel... it was unbelievable.
title: Czech Hunter 194
